{"tid":2131960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"8.3清場案 男速龍身壓女被告直至停止反抗 稱脫掉豬咀才知是女子","createTime":"2020-07-30T07:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T12:21:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8e8b0aa943f596f9f9486ddcd49f1d2c2fa056","tid":2131960,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T07:17:07.000Z","msg":"警員16204盧志聰（音）<br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/50165331718_56080c5548_k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F50165331718_56080c5548_k.jpg&h=2b97efb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）去年8月3日的「旺角再遊行」，入夜後有大批示威者於旺角區設置路障，9人被控非法集結罪，在九龍城裁判法院續審。拘捕其中一名女被告的男性速龍供稱，自己仆倒再起身後，見到前面戴頭盔和眼罩的女子倒地，於是上前壓着她，直至她停止反抗。速龍解釋稱，脱掉其「豬咀」和眼罩才知道被捕人是女子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075953&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=91e1ec8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075953&h=417177d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075953</a>"},{"pid":"fdbc7bcb9c93099b4ce2b3903cb90fbbf4fd0916","tid":2131960,"uid":241804,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T07:18:04.000Z","msg":"乜撚呀，佢用屎眼嚟睇嘢㗎，咁撚樣都up得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla